[p 
	"Contra - The Hard Corps is a game about a wolf that is supposed to save the world from evil robots. Half way through he gets bored of running around and decides to time travel and marry a monkey.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Seriously though, this is an improvement to the existing, and quite old, Contra 4 run. I made a bunch of changes, and all were for the better I think.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"First, I changed the ROM to the Japan version because in this version you get hit points (weird) which allows me to take damage to save time.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Second, I used the wolf. My main reason for this should become quite obvious halfway through the first level. Hint -- pay careful attention to the spider mid boss in level 1, he is the only boss who gets a chance to attack me. The rest of the bosses are killed before they can do anything useful.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Third, I chose to get the secret ending. This game has 6 endings I think. Four are normal, one is really a game over, and this one. I went for this one because you can get it the quickest, and I think the rest of the levels are boring. Going the path I went, one of the later levels has a long auto scrolling part with some kind of swinging thing that attacks you. While it looks funny, I think it's boring.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"This is my third attempt at doing this game, and I hope you like it. By the way I like Contra games.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Goals:
	$LF
]p
[ul 
	[li 
		" Aims for fastest time
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Takes damage to save time
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Achieves best ending :)
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[p 
	"If possible to pick a screen shot for this game, I really like at the end when the wolf is holding his gun up and the words "You Win" are displayed.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"Enjoy
	$LF
]p
