[p 
	"Then there is the problem of obsoletion and categories. People does not seem to want to obsolete the current movie because they have very different endings.
	$LF
	"We can not have one movie per ending, 5 movies for one game is too much.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	"My suggestion is to have one movie for the secret ending (this one), and one movie for any of the 4 "real" endings. Whether that should be the shortest path (current published movie) or the "best" ending (with the rocket in the final stage) is left open at this point.
	$LF
